BioClues, TMS Foundation, and Galaxy India are sponsoring a webinar Saturday, 29th May at 18:00 Indian Time:

  • Git and Its Use in Galaxy
  • Presented by Kiran K Telukunta

Please join us this Saturday on Google Meet.
